column5: Hey Cliff  I went to the doctor today because i had a little problem(things were kind of burning) anyway he gave me something to clear it up You need to go get checked by a doctor I think a Public health nurse will be giving you a call as well!!!!!!   just kidding I have something for you just give me the weekend to check out the new rig and the old girl is all yours let me know how you want to do this I work up by the airport maybe we can meet somewhere and exchange the goods!!!!!  Peter
Ahem.....jeez...you call this being discreet?  I'll call the doc asap.  Just let me know what day and when and I'll come by and see you....preferably after 4pm if possible?
Now this is something that should get LOCKED. HAHAHAHAHAHA Cliff,dont forget the rubber gloves.
Yah..  no worries Cliff.  One dose and bubye nasties!!!  You may need to get in touch with your past partners though.  Roy, I'm looking in your direction..  HAHAAH  HD
EEEEWWWWHHHH! Now I gotta go wash my mouse hand.  JF
